%% Evidence: APS-E001, APS-E002, APS-E003, APS-E006, APS-E008, APS-E009, APS-E015
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Anonymous
  Anonymous --> RegisteredUnverified: POST /api/register
  RegisteredUnverified --> VerifiedUser: verify email token
  Anonymous --> Authenticated: credentials or verified OAuth login
  VerifiedUser --> Authenticated: login
  Authenticated --> PasswordInvalidated: password reset or change
  PasswordInvalidated --> Anonymous: protected route redirect to login
  Authenticated --> Suspended: admin or account delete tombstone
  Suspended --> LimitedAccess: protected write/page blocked
  Authenticated --> DeletedTombstone: delete account
  DeletedTombstone --> Anonymous: sign out
